01:01:52,040 --> 01:01:52,860
I'll write it down in a minute.

1635
01:01:53,200 --> 01:01:54,340
If it's radiation,

1636
01:01:54,340 --> 01:01:56,820
it decreases in another way.

1637
01:01:57,580 --> 01:01:59,740
So how row depends on A

