2041
01:16:56,340 --> 01:16:56,960
It doesn't matter.

2042
01:16:57,760 --> 01:16:59,340
And it has some energy in it.

2043
01:16:59,520 --> 01:17:00,380
The energy,

2044
01:17:00,380 --> 01:17:01,380
of course,

2045
01:17:01,380 --> 01:17:02,400
